&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>Image gallery</title><link>https://demo.stack.jimmycai.com/p/image-gallery/</link><pubDate>Sat, 26 Aug 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://demo.stack.jimmycai.com/p/image-gallery/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://demo.stack.jimmycai.com/p/image-gallery/2.jpg" alt="Featured image of post Image gallery" />&lt;p>Hugo theme Stack supports the creation of interactive image galleries using Markdown. It&amp;rsquo;s powered by &lt;a class="link" href="https://photoswipe.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>PhotoSwipe&lt;/a> and its syntax was inspired by &lt;a class="link" href="https://typlog.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Typlog&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>To use this feature, the image must be in the same directory as the Markdown file, as it uses Hugo&amp;rsquo;s page bundle feature to read the dimensions of the image. &lt;strong>External images are not supported.&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="syntax">Syntax
&lt;/h2>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
